<author>Thangngur</author>
<title>Nau Bang Ei Puiin</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Kanaan gamthak lam chu zuonin,
 Gamthipa khuol ka zin; ziet leh veia tuonglam vaiin;
 Mei leh meipi'n kilak in,
 Ka maah Nang ni bang vakin.

[V2]
 Aw ei Hukampa naubang ei puiin,
 Kanaan gam tun loh ka lau ie;
 Lungngaih lummei zing nuoiah,
 Kap leh mauin albang ka vai.

[V3]
 2 Gamthipa lumsuongpi sunga, damtui thieng hung put hen;
 Kanaan zuon zaitha chawl dawn ding,
 Gamthipa ka chamsung in,
 Aigupta lunga ngilhna di'n.

[V4]
 3. Ka maah zatam a lut tau, Kanaan gam thak a chun;
 Bangdin em nungtieng ka ngaih ding ?
 Thihna gam thuong nungsieh in,
 Hinna vangkhawpi zuon ingka.

[V5]
 4. Chung si-al in thangvan zawlah, Lalpa a chawian ui;
 A gimtheih nau cheng ngilh zo in,
 Nunnawpna la thak a sau,
 Vabang buol ding chu ka nuom ngei!</lyrics>
</song>